data.description: 2.625% APR available for VA eligible buyers!! Remarkable, updated 3 bedroom home in highly desirable, and walkable, Trolly Square neighborhood of Wilmington.  Enter into this lovely, single family home to find contemporary finishes in the form of refinished wood flooring, granite counters, stainless appliances, cable railing, fresh paint, contemporary bathrooms and new carpet.  This one is ready for immediate occupancy.  The real magic is the proximity to dining, shopping, social, and I-95 for ease of commuting.  Call today.
